'''deegree''' supplies the building blocks of a [[Spatial Data Infrastructure]], while implementing the standards of the [[Open Geospatial Consortium|Open Geospatial Consortium (OGC)]] and [[ISO/TC 211]]. The [[Java (programming language)|Java]]-based deegree framework is the most extensive implementation of OGC/ISO standards in the field of Free Software.

The software graduated a [[OSGeo]] project as of January 4, 2012.

==External links==
*{{official website|http://www.deegree.org/}}
*[http://www.osgeo.org/deegree OSGeo project page]
*[https://www.ohloh.net/p/deegree Ohloh project overview]

