07-05-11LagoEnriquilloDR.jpg|[[Lake Enriquillo|Lago Enriquillo]] on [[Hispaniola]] is the lowest point of the [[Dominican Republic]] and all ocean islands.
BadwaterBasin2.JPG|The [[Badwater Basin]] in [[Death Valley]] is the lowest point of the United States and North America.
