'''Rakhine Yoma Elephant Range''' is a wildlife reserve of [[Myanmar]].<ref>[http://www.gms-eoc.org/uploads/resources/546/attachment/2.1.2.%20Case%20Study-Rakhine%20Yoma%20Elephant%20Range.pdf Case study on Rakhine Yoma]</ref> The reserve is located on the [[Arakan Mountains|Arakan mountain range]] in the south west of Myanmar.<ref>[http://sstmyanmar.com/ecotourism/rakhine_yoma.html Location of the reserve]</ref>

